name: Celestial Fang Glider
text: In the twilight grove, the Celestial Fang Glider, harbinger of dreams, unfurled its opal wings. Each beat scattered stardust, weaving magic into the night. With teeth bared in a grin, it danced on starlight streams, a guardian of the realm between waking and the unseen, ever elusive, ever gleaming.
